                     <interp inst="t17830910-72-off406" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17830910-72-cd407" type="crimeDate">29th day of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830910-72-off406 t17830910-72-cd407"></join> last, one linen shirt, value 7 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17830910-72-victim873" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Leonard
                  <interp inst="t17830910-72-victim873" type="surname" value="Leonard"></interp>
